title: Join the 2 Percent, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO22
description: Everyone believes the competition in business is fierce.  But if you think you face overwhelming odds, you're wrong.  According to Andy Frisella, only about two people in a hundred actually have what it takes to press on and finish what they started.  Will you join the 2 percent?
